  "response": "There are several legal ways to access Marvel comics for free or at a reduced cost:\n\n1. Marvel Unlimited\n- Subscription service with thousands of comics\n- First month is often free\n- Monthly or annual subscription options\n\n2. Public Libraries\n- Many libraries offer digital comic services like Hoopla\n- Free access to Marvel comics with library card\n\n3. Free Comic Book Day\n- Annual event where comic shops give away free comics\n- Usually held in May\n\n4. Digital platforms\n- Comixology sometimes offers free Marvel comics\n- Marvel's official website occasionally has free issues\n\n5. Official Marvel website\n- Sometimes offers free preview issues\n- Limited time promotions\n\n6. Free comic apps\n- Apps like Marvel Comics sometimes have free issues\n- Varies by current promotions\n\nAvoid illegal download sites, as they are unauthorized and potentially harmful to your device.\n\nRemember that most free options will have limited selections compared to paid subscriptions.",
